<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرِثُوا الْكِتَابَ}</span> ... أَخَذُوهُ مِنْ أَسْلَافِهِمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَرَضَ هَذَا الأدْنَى}</span> ... مَا يُعْرَضُ لَهُمْ مِنْ دَنِيءِ الْمَكَاسِبِ؛ كَالرِّشْوَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِّيثَاقُ الْكِتَابِ}</span> ... الْعُهُودُ فِي التَّوْرَاةِ؛ بِإِقَامَتِهَا، وَالْعَمَلِ بِهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَدَرَسُوا مَا فِيهِ}</span> ... عَلِمُوا مَا فِي الْكِتَابِ، فَضَيَّعُوهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُمَسِّكُونَ}</span> ... يَتَمَسَّكُونَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَتَقْنَا}</span> ... رَفَعْنَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ظُلَّةٌ}</span> ... سَحَابَةٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَظَنُّوا}</span> ... أَيْقَنُوا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَشْهَدَهُمْ عَلَى أَنفُسِهِمْ}</span> ... قَرَّرَهُمْ بِمَا أَوْدَعَ فِي فِطَرِهِمْ مِنْ تَوْحِيدِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن تَقُولُوا}</span> ... لِئَلَّا تَقُولُوا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذُرِّيَّةً}</span> ... صِغَارًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَانسَلَخَ مِنْهَا}</span> ... خَرَجَ مِنْهَا بِكُفْرِهِ، وَنَبَذَهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَتْبَعَهُ الشَّيْطَانُ}</span> ... لَحِقَهُ، وَصَارَ قَرِينَهُ، وَاسْتَحْوَذَ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَخْلَدَ إِلَى الأَرْضِ}</span> ... رَكَنَ إِلَى الدُّنْيَا، وَرَضِيَ بِهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَحْمِلْ عَلَيْهِ}</span> ... تَطْرُدْهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
